General.Name: Embellence Group AB
General.Description: Embellence Group AB (publ) acquires, owns, and develops various brands in wallpapers, textiles, rugs, and other interior decoration items. It offers its products under the Cole & Son, Wall&decò, Pappelina, Artscape, and Boråstapeter brand names. The company serves customers in Sweden, Norway, Italy, and the United Kingdom. Embellence Group AB (publ) was founded in 1905 and is headquartered in Borås, Sweden.
